{"tid":2406062,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃大仙元辰殿今重開拜太歲","createTime":"2021-02-13T01:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T02:26:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"228c5581353b41746825aa06a49bdd9e1271ab62","tid":2406062,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T01:43:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210213/CZMANAWESJCMBPZQDDYFSKDT2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210213%2FCZMANAWESJCMBPZQDDYFSKDT2Y%2F&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ4WZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=86265c67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210213%2FCZMANAWESJCMBPZQDDYFSKDT2Y%2F&h=328de729\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210213/CZMANAWESJCMBPZQDDYFSKDT2Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n黃大仙元辰殿今重開拜太歲<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ayrrKIOOEBciI3oaIMNmjDUZ5OE=/2362x1575/filters:quality\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FayrrKIOOEBciI3oaIMNmjDUZ5OE%3D%2F2362x1575%2Ffilters%3Aquality&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ4WZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=370897aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FayrrKIOOEBciI3oaIMNmjDUZ5OE%3D%2F2362x1575%2Ffilters%3Aquality&h=0120901b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ayrrKIOOEBciI3oaIMNmjDUZ5OE=/2362x1575/filters:quality</a>(100)/<a href=\"http://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KSS4B2EUGVFRZHRT4ELUY6XECU.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKSS4B2EUGVFRZHRT4ELUY6XECU.jpg&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ4WZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=4f1ffdb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KSS4B2EUGVFRZHRT4ELUY6XECU.jpg</a></span><br />\n■黃大仙祠因應疫情取消年卅晚頭炷香，大批善信改在昨日上香祈福。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】黃大仙祠因應疫情取消年卅晚頭炷香，拜太歲的元辰殿昨日亦未開放。不過祠方表示，太歲元辰殿今日重開，生肖屬牛、羊、狗、馬、龍的善信憑有效身份證明文件免費進入。殿內實施人流管制，上限100人。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：50辣車放煙花狂飆 當警無到<br />\n<br />\n未能按傳統在年卅晚與大仙見面的善信，昨日改在大年初一到場祈福。雖然只准以大會派發的三支香拜神，亦實施人流管制措施，但黃大仙祠仍然人煙鼎沸。有善信認為心意比香燭重要，祈求香港能否極泰來，疫潮盡快過去。<br />\n<br />\n按照人流管制措施，善信要先要在祠外廣場登記，在鐵馬陣步行約五分鐘到櫃枱，再掃瞄「安心出行」二維碼或填表登記，方獲派籌號進入黃大仙祠。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：民間「煙花滙」炮仗聲四起<br />\n<br />\n記者昨早10時入場，由廣場走到殿內大約要花20分鐘。祠內只能以大會派發的三支香拜神，不少善信自攜香燭入場，但無處燃點。在場職員不斷呼籲善信切勿停留，完成儀式後盡快離開。至中午12時半，祠外人潮之多，更需截龍分批放行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不准點私香 商販嘆生意差<br />\n<br />\n從事「打小人」多年的鵝頸橋融姑特地趁年初一來拜黃大仙，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過，在黃大仙祠外售賣香燭用品的負責人彭小姐投訴，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於另一祈福熱點沙田車公廟，土。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JW7Vumu2pGIdw2umMw4iYUbBz3k=/967x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O52PQ4TU75FUREGTDNQQG5QAHA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJW7Vumu2pGIdw2umMw4iYUbBz3k%3D%2F967x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO52PQ4TU75FUREGTDNQQG5QAHA.jpg&h=8d5dec12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有善信求籤，盼獲大仙指點迷津。"},{"pid":"afefd2a03ceec6d17653ecd21412c6d0030aa988","tid":2406062,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T01:49:55.000Z","msg":"真係多迷信on9"},{"pid":"7a4614a88ee3a7c315adc34d75d9ff51e4669993","tid":2406062,"uid":360811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T02:26:15.000Z","msg":"香港的善信們<br />\n新一年誠心祈求:<br />\n香港要真.雙普選!"}]}